des: Bill Spadea is diggin’ in, with ideas and perspective about the most important issues facing New Jersey today. Bill, the morning host for New Jersey 101.5, knows what matters to the people of the great Garden State — and he’s watching out for them. Bill breaks down the issues quickly every morning so you can start your day informed.
